        &trans  &mt LCTRL UNDER       &mt LEFT_ALT ASTERISK  &mt LEFT_SHIFT PLUS  &trans    &kp SINGLE_QUOTE   &mt LS(NUMBER_4) KP_NUMBER_4  &mt LEFT_GUI KP_NUMBER_3  &mt LCTRL KP_NUMBER_2  &mt LEFT_GUI KP_NUMBER_1
&trans  &trans  &kp NON_US_BACKSLASH  &kp SLASH              &kp MINUS            &trans    &kp KP_NUMBER_8    &kp KP_NUMBER_7               &kp KP_NUMBER_6           &kp KP_NUMBER_5        &trans                    &trans
